  "texts": [
    "Garments in the virtual world are a set of data that can make people feel comfortable in various activities.",
    "In addition, in the real world, a consumer must wear a heavily padded coat to stay warm, whereas in the Metaverse, clothing can automatically regulate body temperature, which makes it possible to wear lighter-looking clothing in cold places.",
    "Clothing in the Metaverse has the potential to overcome the physical constraints of the real world.",
    "Under these conditions, designers can boldly use their imagination to create astonishing fashion items that could not be made in the real world.",
    "Although designers may be inspired by many things in the real world, they cannot carry out an objective evaluation of clothing at the design stage; they typically first need to create a sketch of a garment and produce a physical sample before they can objectively evaluate it."
